(1, 'Contest Prizes', 'prize-details', 'prize-details', '<p>One (1) Grand Prize Contest winner will receive $5,000; prize will be awarded as a cheque.</p>\r\n<p>Six (6) Weekly Prize Contest Winners will receive a $150 gift card (from a National Retailer) and a BIC Product Prize pack valued at $50.00 each.</p>\r\n<p><a title="Click here for Official Rules" href="/bic-ffyw/page/official-rules">Click here for Official Rules</a></p>', '1', '2016-07-20 11:25:43', '2016-07-20 11:25:43', '2016-07-20 11:25:43', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(2, 'PRIX DU CONCOURS', 'prize-details', 'prize-details', '<p>Un (1) gagnant du grand prix du concours recevra 5&nbsp;000&nbsp;$, remis sous forme de ch&egrave;que.</p>\r\n<p>Six (6) gagnants du concours hebdomadaire remporteront une carte-cadeau de 150 $ (d''un d&eacute;taillant national) et un lot de produits BIC d''une valeur de 50 $ chacun.</p>\r\n<p><a title="R&egrave;glements officiel" href="/bic-ffyw/fr/page/official-rules">Cliqez ici pour le r&egrave;glement officiel</a></p>', '3', '2016-07-20 11:26:35', '2016-07-20 11:26:35', '2016-07-20 11:26:35', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(3, 'Tip 1', 'tip-1', 'tip-1', '<p>Reduce emails and connect with family and friends by sending them handwritten notes and birthday cards throughout the year.</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:15:07', '2016-07-22 09:15:07', '2016-07-22 09:15:07', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(4, 'Tip 1', 'tip-1', 'tip-1', '<p>R&eacute;duisez le nombre de courriels avec la famille et les amis en leur envoyant des notes &eacute;crites &agrave; la main et des cartes de naissance au cours de l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e.</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 09:15:54', '2016-07-22 09:15:54', '2016-07-22 09:15:54', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(5, 'Tip 2', 'tip-2', 'tip-2', '<p>Handwrite a letter together as a family, describing where you hope to be in five years. It&rsquo;s a great keepsake to look back at your children&rsquo;s handwriting and how it has progressed&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:30:58', '2016-07-22 09:30:58', '2016-07-22 09:30:58', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(6, 'Tip 2', 'tip-2', 'tip-2', '<p>&Eacute;crivez &agrave; la main une lettre &agrave; titre de projet en famille, en d&eacute;crivant o&ugrave; vous voulez vous rendre dans l&rsquo;espace de cinq ans. Cela vous fournira un superbe souvenir &agrave; lire r&eacute;trospectivement &agrave; l&rsquo;avenir et vous pourrez voir les progr&egrave;s de l&rsquo;&eacute;criture &agrave; la main de vos enfants.</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 09:31:20', '2016-07-22 09:31:20', '2016-07-22 09:31:20', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(7, 'Tip 3', 'tip-3', 'tip-3', '<p>Encourage parents and grandparents to handwrite their children/ grandchildren&rsquo;s favourite story in a journal as a keepsake for when the children get older.</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:32:42', '2016-07-22 09:32:42', '2016-07-22 09:32:42', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(8, 'Tip 3', 'tip-3', 'tip-3', '<p>Encouragez les parents et les grands-parents &agrave; consigner dans un journal des histoires favourites &agrave; propos de leurs enfants ou petits-enfants comme souvenir &agrave; c&eacute;l&eacute;brer quand les enfants seront plus grands.</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 09:33:07', '2016-07-22 09:33:07', '2016-07-22 09:33:07', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(9, 'Tip 4', 'tip-4', 'tip-4', '<p>Include a handwritten note in your spouse&rsquo;s suitcase before a business trip and your child&rsquo;s lunchbox or overnight bag for their first sleepover.</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:33:45', '2016-07-22 09:33:45', '2016-07-22 09:33:45', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(11, 'Tip 5', 'tip-5', 'tip-5', '<p>Why wait until Valentine&rsquo;s Day? &nbsp;Write a love note to your loved one &ndash; a personal way to show how much you care.</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:35:48', '2016-07-22 09:35:48', '2016-07-22 09:35:48', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(12, 'Tip 5', 'tip-5', 'tip-5', '<p>Pourquoi attendre jusqu''&agrave; la Saint-Valentin? &Eacute;crivez un mot d''amour &agrave; votre bien-aim&eacute;(e) pour lui montrer de mani&egrave;re personnelle combien il/elle vous est cher/ch&egrave;re.</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 09:36:18', '2016-07-22 09:36:18', '2016-07-22 09:36:18', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(13, 'Tip 6', 'tip-6', 'tip-6', '<p>Stay connected during family vacations and send postcards to loved ones so they know you were thinking of them and sharing your vacation memories</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:36:58', '2016-07-22 09:36:58', '2016-07-22 09:36:58', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(14, 'Tip 6', 'tip-6', 'tip-6', '<p>Restez en communication pendant les vacances familiales&nbsp;: envoyez des cartes postales &agrave; vos proches pour qu&rsquo;ils savent que vous pensez &agrave; eux et pour partager des souvenirs de vacances.</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 09:37:44', '2016-07-22 09:37:44', '2016-07-22 09:37:44', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(15, 'Tip 7', 'tip-7', 'tip-7', '<p>Start a diary or journal to record memorable occasions. Try and write daily about little anecdotes about your day.&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:39:44', '2016-07-22 09:39:44', '2016-07-22 09:39:44', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(16, 'Tip 7', 'tip-7', 'tip-7', '<p>Commencez &agrave; tenir un journal pour documenter les occasions m&eacute;morables. Essayez de noter chaque jour les petites anecdotes sur votre journ&eacute;e.</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 09:40:58', '2016-07-22 09:40:58', '2016-07-22 09:40:58', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(17, 'Tip 8', 'tip-8', 'tip-8', '<p>Keep a pen and pad of paper by your bed at night. Write down any ideas you have through the night so you can clear your mind and have restful, worry-free sleep.</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:41:47', '2016-07-22 09:41:47', '2016-07-22 09:41:47', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(18, 'Tip 8', 'tip-8', 'tip-8', '<p>La nuit, gardez un stylo et un bloc-notes &agrave; votre chevet. Notez toutes les id&eacute;es qui vous viennent &agrave; l&rsquo;esprit durant la nuit pour vous lib&eacute;rer l''esprit et avoir un sommeil r&eacute;parateur sans soucis.</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 09:43:23', '2016-07-22 09:43:23', '2016-07-22 09:43:23', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(19, 'Tip 9', 'tip-9', 'tip-9', '<p>Set aside specific times during the week for writing stories, songs or even jokes. Let your kids use their imaginations.</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:44:06', '2016-07-22 09:44:06', '2016-07-22 09:44:06', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(20, 'Tip 9', 'tip-9', 'tip-9', '<p>R&eacute;servez des temps sp&eacute;cifiques durant la semaine pour &eacute;crire des histoires, des chansons ou des farces. Encouragez vos enfants &agrave; donner libre cours &agrave; leur imagination!&nbsp;</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 09:45:33', '2016-07-22 09:45:33', '2016-07-22 09:45:33', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(21, 'Tip 10', 'tip-10', 'tip-10', '<p>Have an assortment of colorful pens, pencils and markers on hand that will make kids want to spend more time writing.</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:47:27', '2016-07-22 09:47:27', '2016-07-22 09:47:27', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(22, 'Tip 10', 'tip-10', 'tip-10', '<p>Assurez-vous de disposer d&rsquo;une vari&eacute;t&eacute; de stylos, de crayons et de marqueurs color&eacute;s pour inspirer les jeunes &agrave; consacrer plus de temps &agrave; l''&eacute;criture.</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 09:49:16', '2016-07-22 09:49:16', '2016-07-22 09:49:16', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(23, 'Tip 11', 'tip-11', 'tip-11', '<p>Make writing special for kids with their own personal table, desk, or designated area. Get them excited about their own writing space!</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:50:06', '2016-07-22 09:50:06', '2016-07-22 09:50:06', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(24, 'Tip 11', 'tip-11', 'tip-11', '<p>Faites de l&rsquo;&eacute;criture une activit&eacute; sp&eacute;ciale pour les enfants en donnant &agrave; chacun sa propre table, son propre pupitre ou son endroit d&eacute;sign&eacute;. Suscitez leur enthousiasme d&rsquo;avoir un espace d&rsquo;&eacute;criture personnel!</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 09:50:58', '2016-07-22 09:50:58', '2016-07-22 09:50:58', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(25, 'Tip 12', 'tip-12', 'tip-12', '<p>Give kids a fun assignment that requires them to write. Make a birthday wish list or write a letter to someone famous.</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:52:01', '2016-07-22 09:52:01', '2016-07-22 09:52:01', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(26, 'Tip 12', 'tip-12', 'tip-12', '<p>Donnez aux enfants un travail d&rsquo;&eacute;criture amusant &agrave; ex&eacute;cuter, comme, par exemple, la r&eacute;daction d&rsquo;une liste de souhaits pour leur f&ecirc;te ou d&rsquo;une lettre &agrave; une personnalit&eacute; c&eacute;l&egrave;bre.&nbsp;</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 09:54:14', '2016-07-22 09:54:14', '2016-07-22 09:54:14', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(27, 'Tip 13', 'tip-13', 'tip-13', '<p>Make up games around writing. Have your kids practice signing their autographs to give to mom or dad.&nbsp;</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:55:19', '2016-07-22 09:55:19', '2016-07-22 09:55:19', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(28, 'Tip 13', 'tip-13', 'tip-13', '<p>Inventez des jeux d&rsquo;&eacute;criture. Les jeunes peuvent se pratiquer &agrave; signer leur autographe pour la donner &agrave; Maman ou &agrave; Papa.</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 09:56:39', '2016-07-22 09:56:39', '2016-07-22 09:56:39', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(29, 'Tip 14', 'tip-14', 'tip-14', '<p>Create a handwritten list to keep track of all the exciting stuff you want to accomplish in life! &nbsp;Encourage family members to add to the list.</p>', '1', '2016-07-22 09:59:27', '2016-07-22 09:59:27', '2016-07-22 09:59:27', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(30, 'Tip 14', 'tip-14', 'tip-14', '<p>Cr&eacute;ez une liste &eacute;crite &agrave; la main pour documenter tous les exploits que vous souhaitez r&eacute;aliser dans la vie. Encouragez les membres de famille &agrave; en ajouter d&rsquo;autres &agrave; la liste.</p>', '3', '2016-07-22 10:01:23', '2016-07-22 10:01:23', '2016-07-22 10:01:23', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(31, 'Browser Outdated', 'out-date-browser', 'out-date-browser', '<p>It looks like your browser is outdated. To access this site, you need to use one of the following browsers:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Internet Explorer&reg; 9 or higher</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Firefox&reg; 45 or higher</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Google&reg; Chrome 49 or higher</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Opera&reg; 36&nbsp;or higher</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Apple&reg; Safari&trade; 6 or higher (Mac)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Please consider upgrading your browser.</p>', '1', '2016-07-24 12:41:16', '2016-07-24 12:41:16', '2016-07-24 12:41:16', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(32, 'Version du navigateur obsolète', 'out-date-browser', 'out-date-browser', '<p>Il semble que votre navigateur ne soit plus &agrave; jour. Pour acc&eacute;der &agrave; ce site, vous devez utiliser l&rsquo;une des versions de navigateur suivantes :</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Internet Explorer&reg; 9 ou version plus r&eacute;cente</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Firefox&reg; 45 ou version plus r&eacute;cente</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Google&reg; Chrome 49 ou version plus r&eacute;cente</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Opera&reg; 36&nbsp;ou version plus r&eacute;cente</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Apple&reg; Safari&trade; 6 ou version plus r&eacute;cente (Mac)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Veuillez envisager de mettre votre navigateur &agrave; niveau.</p>', '3', '2016-07-24 12:41:59', '2016-07-24 12:41:59', '2016-07-24 12:41:59', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(33, 'Boys And Girls Clubs Of Canada', 'boys-and-girls-clubs-of-canada', 'boys-and-girls-clubs-of-canada', '<div class="contents">\r\n<div class="doodle doodle_1"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/doodle_bic_helping_1.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="doodle doodle_2"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/doodle_bic_helping_2.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="doodle doodle_3"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/doodle_bic_helping_3.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="pencil_image pencil_2"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/pencil_2.png" alt="Pencil" /></div>\r\n<div class="pencil_image pencil_3"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/pencil_3.png" alt="Pencil" /></div>\r\n<h3>How BIC is Helping</h3>\r\n<div class="logos"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/BGCC_Logo.png" alt="Boys and Girls Club of Canada" /></div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-offset-2">\r\n<p>Join thousands of Canadians and support BIC''s FFYW mission by participating in our weekly challenges! For every submission, BIC will donate $10 to the Boys and Girls Clubs of Canada and enter you into a grand prize draw to win $5,000 towards your child''s education!*&nbsp;<br /><small>(*Donation up to a maximum of $10,000)</small>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<a class="button_blue" href="https://www.bgccan.com/EN/Pages/default.aspx" target="_blank">LEARN MORE ABOUT BOYS AND GIRLS CLUBS OF CANADA</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '1', '2016-07-26 06:25:44', '2016-07-26 06:25:44', '2016-07-26 06:25:44', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(34, 'Repaires jeunesse du Canada', 'boys-and-girls-clubs-of-canada', 'boys-and-girls-clubs-of-canada', '<div class="contents">\r\n<div class="doodle doodle_1"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/doodle_bic_helping_1.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="doodle doodle_2"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/doodle_bic_helping_2.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="doodle doodle_3"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/doodle_bic_helping_3.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="pencil_image pencil_2"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/pencil_2.png" alt="Pencil" /></div>\r\n<div class="pencil_image pencil_3"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/pencil_3.png" alt="Pencil" /></div>\r\n<h3>Comment BIC apporte son soutien</h3>\r\n<div class="logos"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/BGCC_Logo_French.jpg" alt="Repaires jeunesse du Canada" /></div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-offset-2">\r\n<p>Rejoignez les milliers de canadiens qui soutiennent d&eacute;j&agrave; la mission FFYW de BIC en participant &agrave; nos d&eacute;fis hebdomadaires! &Agrave; chaque participation, BIC fera un don de 10&nbsp;$ aux Repaires jeunesse du Canada et vous serez automatiquement inscrit au grand un tirage au sort pour tenter de gagner 5&nbsp;000&nbsp;$ &agrave; d&eacute;dier aux &eacute;tudes de votre enfant!*</p>\r\n<p><small>(*Dons jusqu''&agrave; un maximum de 10 000 $)</small></p>\r\n<a class="button_blue" href="https://www.bgccan.com/FR/Pages/default.aspx" target="_blank">En apprendre davantage sur les Repaires jeunesse du Canada</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '3', '2016-07-26 06:27:51', '2016-07-26 06:27:51', '2016-07-26 06:27:51', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(35, 'Écrivez dès maintenant', 'write-now', 'write-now', '<div class="contents">\r\n<div class="doodle doodle_1"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/doodle_write_now_1.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="doodle doodle_2"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/doodle_write_now_2.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="doodle doodle_3"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/doodle_write_now_3.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n<h3>&Eacute;crivez d&egrave;s maintenant!</h3>\r\n<h4 class="subtitle">C&eacute;l&eacute;brez l&rsquo;&eacute;criture avec des activit&eacute;s rigolos et cr&eacute;atives!</h4>\r\n<div class="row no_gutter">\r\n<div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-offset-1">\r\n<h5>CINQ TRUCS</h5>\r\n<h6>con&ccedil;us pour inspirer les enfants &agrave; &eacute;crire</h6>\r\n<p>1. R&eacute;servez des temps sp&eacute;cifiques durant la semaine pour &eacute;crire des histoires, des chansons ou des farces. Encouragez vos enfants &agrave; donner libre cours &agrave; leur imagination!</p>\r\n<p>2. Assurez-vous de disposer d&rsquo;une vari&eacute;t&eacute; de stylos, de crayons et de marqueurs color&eacute;s pour inspirer les jeunes &agrave; consacrer plus de temps &agrave; l''&eacute;criture.</p>\r\n<p>3. Faites de l&rsquo;&eacute;criture une activit&eacute; sp&eacute;ciale pour les enfants en donnant &agrave; chacun sa propre table, son propre pupitre ou son endroit d&eacute;sign&eacute;. Suscitez leur enthousiasme d&rsquo;avoir un espace d&rsquo;&eacute;criture personnel!</p>\r\n<p>4. Donnez aux enfants un travail d&rsquo;&eacute;criture amusant &agrave; ex&eacute;cuter, comme, par exemple, la r&eacute;daction d&rsquo;une liste de souhaits pour leur f&ecirc;te ou d&rsquo;une lettre &agrave; une personnalit&eacute; c&eacute;l&egrave;bre.</p>\r\n<p>5. Inventez des jeux d&rsquo;&eacute;criture. Les jeunes peuvent se pratiquer &agrave; signer leur autographe pour la donner &agrave; Maman ou &agrave; Papa.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2"><img class="vertical_divider" src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/divider_2.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4">\r\n<div class="downloadable">\r\n<div class="get_list">Obtenez ici votre Liste de magasinage <em>t&eacute;l&eacute;chargeable</em> pour la rentr&eacute;e des classes!</div>\r\n<div><a class="button_blue" href="/bic-ffyw/uploads/BIC_BackToSchool_Checklist-fr.pdf" target="_blank">T&Eacute;L&Eacute;CHARGER</a></div>\r\n<div class="pencil_purple"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/pencil_purple.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '3', '2016-07-26 06:40:04', '2016-07-26 06:40:04', '2016-07-26 06:40:04', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(36, 'Product - NOT USE', 'product', 'product', '<div class="contents">\r\n<div class="doodle doodle_1"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/doodle_products_1.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="doodle doodle_2"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/doodle_products_2.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-10 col-md-10 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-offset-1">\r\n<h2>PRODUCTS</h2>\r\n<h3>BIC<sup>&reg;&nbsp;</sup>PRODUCTS MAKE WRITING FUN!</h3>\r\n<div><a href="../../en/product/pencil"><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/products_intro.png" alt="Introducing BIC Extra-fun pencils Click here" /></a></div>\r\n<p>The perfect BIC<sup>&reg;</sup> pen, pencil or marker can make a child feel inspired to write. We offer so much variety and style; kids and adults will be amazed by what they find. Our products offer:</p>\r\n<p>Smooth writing pens and pencils &bull; Bold, classic and fashionable ink colours &bull; Precise writing instruments &bull; Variety of shapes and point sizes for that perfect fit &bull; Incredibly comfortable grips &bull; Forgiving smudge-free and erasable mechanical pencils</p>\r\n<h6>Check out some of our products!</h6>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-1 col-md-1">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="product_types clearfix">\r\n<div class="product_type product_pens">\r\n<div class="product_type_inner">\r\n<div class="title">PENS</div>\r\n<div><img src="http://staging.bicfightforyourwrite.ca.en.matchmgassets.com/themes/default/images/products_pens.png" alt="Pens" /></div>\r\n<div class="description">From ballpoint pen to gel to roller, these awesome varieties of pens provide endless hours of fun writing!</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><a class="learn_more" href="../../en/product/pens">LEARN MORE</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="product_type product_pencils">\r\n<div class="product_t