(57, 'Video Transcript', 'video-transcript', 'video-transcript', '<div class="contents">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-offset-2">\r\n<h1>Video Text Transcript</h1>\r\n<div class="video_container"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yx6tellQ5dk?rel=0&amp;controls=0&amp;showinfo=0;autoplay=0" width="100%" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>\r\n<p>Hey, did you know that writing can make you awesome? The act of handwriting is an essential tool for learning and growth. That&rsquo;s why BiC started a mission to save handwriting. Let&rsquo;s checkout the facts.</p>\r\n<p>Interesting fact number one. Writing helps foster creativity. Look at Brian, writing took him from a pop quick to a pop star.</p>\r\n<p>Interesting fact number two. Writing can help improve critical thinking skills. Helping Meghan fly through finals.</p>\r\n<p>Interesting fact number three. Writing boosts self-confidence. For Lucy here, it took her from class clown to class president.</p>\r\n<p>Interesting fact number four. Better writers make better readers. Writing sent Alex from easy readers to epic novels.</p>\r\n<p>With all of these facts, the importance of handwriting is clear. Together let&rsquo;s see how great writing can be. How great you can be.</p>\r\n<p>Join BiC&rsquo;s mission and Fight For Your Write.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '1', '2016-07-28 16:17:24', '2016-07-28 16:17:24', '2016-07-28 16:17:24', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(58, 'Video Transcript', 'video-transcript', 'video-transcript', '<div class="contents">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-offset-2">\r\n<h1>Transcription des textes vid&eacute;o</h1>\r\n<div class="video_container"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GWpMlfGbj-c?rel=0&amp;controls=0&amp;showinfo=0;autoplay=0" width="100%" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>\r\n<p>Bic est en mission pour sauver l&rsquo;&eacute;criture.</p>\r\n<p>Pourquoi?</p>\r\n<p>&Eacute;crire favorise la cr&eacute;ativit&eacute;. Pour F&eacute;lix, une bonne note l&rsquo;a transform&eacute; en musicien.</p>\r\n<p>&Eacute;crire am&eacute;liore ta capacit&eacute; de r&eacute;flexion &ndash; comme Kellie, qui domine ses examens.</p>\r\n<p>&Eacute;crire augmente la confiance en soi. Lucie est pass&eacute; de clown de classe &agrave; pr&eacute;sidente de classe.</p>\r\n<p>D&eacute;couvre &agrave; quel point l&rsquo;&eacute;criture peut &ecirc;tre g&eacute;niale; &agrave; quel point tu peux &ecirc;tre g&eacute;nial.</p>\r\n<p>Accepte ta mission Bic, et exerce ton pouvoir d&rsquo;&eacute;crire !</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '3', '2016-07-28 16:20:24', '2016-07-28 16:20:24', '2016-07-28 16:20:24', 1, 0, 1, NULL, NULL);

